To generate Debian packages, do:

1. in $JMOL_CVSDIR/jmol type:

   ant -Ddocbook.dir=/usr/share/sgml/docbook/stylesheet/xsl/nwalsh sourcedist.tar.gz
   cp jmol-$VERSION.source.tar.gz /tmp

   where $VERSION is substituted by the current version

2. in $JMOL_CVSDIR/jmol/packaging/debian update for version the files

   VERSION, Makefile, build.xml, changelog

3. in $JMOL_CVSDIR/jmol/packaging/debian type:
   make
